What is CRUD?

Almost every application performs these four operations:

Operation	HTTP Method	Example
Create	POST	Register a student
Read	GET	Get all students
Update	PUT	Update a student's details
Delete	DELETE	Remove a student

Examples:

Instagram → Create a post
WhatsApp → Read messages
Amazon → Update your address
Gmail → Delete an email

These are all CRUD operations.



